OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774980702
OL,3,CCalls for eggs to be swapped for
OL,4,Cpotatoes to 'modernise' Easter event
OL,6,FAn animal rights group is urging a
OL,7,Fcity council to "modernise" their
OL,8,Ffamous Easter egg roll - by swapping
OL,9,Ftraditional hens' eggs for dyed
OL,10,Fpotatoes.
OL,12,FPETA claims the move would be a
OL,13,F"cheaper, healthier, and more animal-
OL,14,Ffriendly" way to celebrate the annual
OL,15,Fevent at Avenham Park, in Preston,
OL,16,Fwhich dates back 150 years.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
