FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774980702
OL,3,CCalls for eggs to be swapped for
OL,4,Cpotatoes to 'modernise' Easter event
OL,6,FIn a letter to Preston City Council,
OL,7,Fthe group argued that a "potato roll"
OL,8,Fwould make the festivities more
OL,9,Finclusive for those who avoid eggs for
OL,10,Fhealth, religious, or environmental
OL,11,Freasons.
OL,13,FThe campaign also focuses heavily on
OL,14,Fthe welfare of the birds.
OL,16,FElisa Allen, from PETA said: "Children
OL,17,Flove animals and would be sad to learn
OL,18,Fthat the eggs used for fun and games
OL,19,Fat Preston's egg rolling event come
OL,20,Ffrom tormented hens who live miserable
OL,21,Flives on Britain's farms.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774980702
OL,3,CCalls for eggs to be swapped for
OL,4,Cpotatoes to 'modernise' Easter event
OL,6,F"Easter should be a time of renewal
OL,7,Fand joy for all sentient beings ` and
OL,8,Fthat means hens, too."
OL,10,FThe charity is highlighting the
OL,11,Fconditions of hens in the UK egg
OL,12,Findustry, alleging that many are
OL,13,Fconfined to "dark, filthy sheds" where
OL,14,Fthey are unable to even stretch their
OL,15,Fwings.
OL,17,FPETA says that even labels like "free-
OL,18,Frange" or "organic" do not guarantee a
OL,19,Fhigh quality of life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
