PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1774980702
OL,3,CCalls for eggs to be swapped for
OL,4,Cpotatoes to 'modernise' Easter event
OL,6,FPreston's egg rolling event is one of
OL,7,Fthe oldest of its kind in the UK,
OL,8,Ftraditionally seeing hundreds of
OL,9,Ffamilies gather to race hard-boiled
OL,10,Feggs down the park's steep slopes.
OL,12,FPreston City Council has not confirmed
OL,13,Fwhether they will consider PETA's
OL,14,Frequest.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
